 Motion Pictures]]\n| Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Viacom18 Motion Pictures]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Vinod Chopra Films]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Vishesh Films]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Dulquer Salmaan|Wayfarer Films]]\n|[[Kochi]]\n|-\n|[[Y NOT Studios]]\n|Chennai\n|-\n|[[Yash Raj Films]]\n| Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Zee Entertainment Enterprises]]\n| Mumbai\n|}\n\n==Music studios==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Name\n! Headquarter\n|-\n|[[Aditya Music ]]\n| Hyderabad\n|-\n|[[Balaji Motion Pictures|Balaji Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Eros Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Madhura Audio]]\n|Hyderabad\n|-\n|[[Pen India Limited|Pen India Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Saregama]] \n|Mumbai\n|-\n| [[Shree Venkatesh Films|SVF Music]]\n| Kolkata\n|-\n|[[Shemaroo Entertainment|Sheemaroo]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Sony Music India|Sony Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Super Cassettes Industries T-Series|T-Series]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Times Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Tips Industries|Tips Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Universal Music India|Universal Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[YRF Music]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Zee Music Company]]\n| Mumbai\n|-\n|}\n\n==Film distributors==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Distributor name\n! Headquarter\n|-\n| [[AA Films]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Dharma Productions]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Dream Factory (distributor)|Dream Factory]]\n|Chennai\n|-\n|[[Eros International]]\n| Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Fox Star Studios]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Lyca Productions]]\n|Chennai\n|-\n|[[Mowgli Productions]]\n|New Delhi\n|-\n|[[T-Series (company)|T-Series]]\n|Mumbai\n|-\n|[[Yash Raj Films]]\n|Mumbai\n|}\n\n==Closed film producing companies==\n*[[Bombay Talkies]], closed in 1953\n*[[R. K. Films]], closed in 2019\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Film production companies in India}}\n[[Category:Indian film-related lists|Production companies]]\n[[Category:Film production companies by country|India]]\n", "text_old": "A film production company is a company that generally produces, creates and distributes [[motion pictures]] (films), musics or other program